A vintage 1960s-style illustration of a man lounging in a rattan peacock chair, surrounded by floating smartphones and mobile devices arranged like a constellation around him, rendered in warm retro colors of mustard yellow, burnt orange, and teal. The scene includes tropical houseplants and a window showing a Singapore cityscape with traditional shophouses. Red paper envelopes are scattered decoratively on a mid-century modern side table. The composition has a warm, leisurely holiday atmosphere with soft halftone dot textures typical of vintage magazine illustrations.
